  "texts": [
    "Wazuh allows users to add new decoders for the logs of their custom data sources.",
    "The decoder files are in XML format and use regular expressions for pattern matching.",
    "In Elastic Security data shippers known as Beats can be used to collect data from new sources.",
    "In OSSIM new plugins can be created for custom data sources.",
    "A unique plugin ID needs to be assigned and the path of the log file for the new data source needs to be configured."
  ],
